gomodel:SYNGO_550  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Electrophysiological evidences show decreased AMPA/NMDA ratio of eEPSCs and enhanced LTP at IRSp53-/- SC-CA1 synapses, compared with WT mice.\n\nFurthermore amplitude but not frequency, of NMDA receptor-mediated mEPSCs is enhanced at IRSp53-/- SC-CA1 synapses and enhanced NMDA receptor-mediated synaptic transmission during the delivery of TBS.. Experimental description: 5-8 weeks mice 129 ola strain" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
